search_results.title: History/heritage
search_results.snippet: In 1970, a Finnish pharmaceutical company Orion-yhtymä Oy introduced LUMENE, a beauty brand inspired by Nordic nature.

search_results.title: Lumene
search_results.snippet: Lumene is a Finnish manufacturer of cosmetics, based in Kauklahti, Espoo. The majority of the Lumene products are developed and manufactured in Finland.
